        <div class="intro">
            <h2>Breast Augmentation</h2>
            <p>this surgery caters to individuals seeking to increase breast size for cosmetic improvement or confidence enhancement. The procedure involves placing implants beneath the breast tissue or chest muscles. Prior to the surgery, patients are thoroughly informed about potential risks and complications by the plastic surgeon.</p>
        </div>
    </div>
<hr>
    <div class="wrapper1">
        <img src="https://www.myplasticsurgeon.ca/images/stahls-bar-spock-ear-and-normal-ear-diagram.jpg" alt="">
        <div class="intro1">
            <h2>Ear Correction</h2>
            <p>this surgery addresses the issue of prominent ears and is often performed on children or teenagers. The procedure not only improves the cosmetic appearance of the ears but also their functionality. It aims to boost the patient's self-image and can correct any ear deformities due to injuries.</p>
        </div>
    </div>
<hr>
    <div class="wrapper2">
        <img src="https://my.clevelandclinic.org/-/scassets/images/org/health/articles/24022-gynecomastia-male-reduction-surgery" alt="">
        <div class="intro2">
            <h2>Gynecomastia</h2>
            <p>This condition occurs in men when there is a noticeable increase in breast tissue, typically stemming from hormonal imbalances involving testosterone and estrogen. The surgical intervention aims to remove excess gland tissue, which can impact one or both breasts. In addition to surgical options, BBMH Hospital provides access to mental health specialists to address any related emotional concerns.</p>
        </div>
    </div>

    <hr>
    <div class="wrapper1">
        <img src="https://drgirirajgandhi.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/06/birth-mark-removal-surgery-01.jpg" alt="">
        <div class="intro1">
            <h2>Surgery for birth/burn marks</h2>
            <p>This kind of surgery is specially done by plastic surgeons to rectify birth defects or burn injury marks. Usually, laser removal of scars is done as it is safe and less invasive. For deeper scars processes such as skin grafts, excision, and dermabrasion are used. This leads to a noticeable improvement in the area that is scarred.</p>
        </div>
    </div>
    <hr><div class="wrapper2">
        <div class="intro2">
            <h2>Vaginal Rejuvenation (Labiaplasty)</h2>
            <p>Labiaplasty is a kind of surgery that is carried out to minimize the length of labia minora. With this surgery, we aim to reduce the asymmetry in thevaginal area. Women go in for this surgery due to self-consciousness, irritation, or itching during intercourse. Complete care and precaution are carried out to ensure the maximum satisfaction of the patient our plastic surgery hospital in bhilwara.</p>
        </div>
    </div>
    
